Power consumption:
This one consumes 3 times more than specified electricity consumption.

Noise:
Annoying rattle coming from behind the refridgerator. It increases when loaded with new objects. And in summer mode it's even more annoying.

Cooling:
Takes too long to cool in lower compartments but it's fine. since it keeps temperature low for reasonably long time. Freezing is done quicker, although it takes more than 1hour.

Design and features:
Design is average. It's a bit hard to open the door sometimes. I almost tilted the fridge when opening one time. And the door compartments come out from slot easily with little force. Blance is off when putting big bottles in the door.
Now for the temperature control, it has only three modes. I don't know if there's any intermediate states since there is no numbers to specify.

Price:
It's a good product for its price. I bought this 20% off from standard price.

Well those are the shortcomings of this product but for it's price it is a good one. If your are at a budget this one is a better choice. If you wanted more features and performance this is not a good choice.

Bought this refrigerator during the big billion sale 2021. First impression is good, however listing few points which are a little bit issue from practical usage perspective -

1. Power cord of the fridge originates from bottom and is barely 6 inch more than height of the fridge. Just a fyi that the height of fridge is only about 4 ft. Generally the power sockets on the wall are at a height of 5 ft. So to use the new fridge, I had to change my electric fittings in order to plug in the fridge. This incurred me another thousand bucks.

2. This fridge has only 2 supporting legs in the front whereas in the rear there is a thin metal compressor casing which touches the ground. So practically the ground clearance is 0. You can never be able to clean the surface below the fridge. Use of a refrigerator plastic stand is inevitable. This incurs another 250 - 300 bucks.

3. There is no installation provided by the company. It is DIY type of purchase.

4. This product is manufactured in China and sold in India by Haeir. I am personally disappointed buying Chinese goods.
